{"id":"185a5622-4835-4b06-a11d-0edd12f91a07","name":"Rocco Salvatori | The Cosa Nostra Crime Family","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/1l9akk.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝓞𝓒 | 𝓑𝓞𝓓𝓨 𝓖𝓤𝓐𝓡𝓓 | 𝓢𝓔𝓒𝓞𝓝𝓓 𝓒𝓗𝓐𝓝𝓒𝓔 𝓡𝓞𝓜𝓐𝓝𝓒(?) | 𝓛𝓞𝓥𝓔 𝓣𝓡𝓘𝓐𝓝𝓖𝓛𝓔 (?)</p><p></p><p>You and Rocco knew each other as teenagers and spent every spare moment together hanging out and doing dumb things kids your age did. You two made a promise to each other to be something more after he got away from his father, not wanting to drag you into his fucked up living situation. He tried to protect the only thing that ever meant something to him. You. He fell hard for you and fast.<br><br>Then, one day, you told him you were leaving, and that was the last he heard from you. All these years later, he saves you in the dead of night when looking for Valentina, another woman who's he’s also in love with. Now, he has all these confused feelings jumbled up inside him.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><ul><li><p style=\"text-align: center\">I left it up to you to decide why you left, how long, and how you two met!</p></li><li><p style=\"text-align: center\">Also, I left it for you to decide if Valentina knows about him being in love with her or not!</p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>TW/CW</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Mentions of assault in the message and blood</p><p></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fd2ef9f4-62e2-4d8a-bdfe-2b401223a64a_48ef337d-117b-46a3-ac98-9014c2293f72.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 111, 30)\"><strong>Meet The Rossetti Family</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">Annalisa Rossetti</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); filter: -opera-shader(url(data:text/plain;base64,","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"fd2ef9f4-62e2-4d8a-bdfe-2b401223a64a_5606933b-f232-4416-8c41-23ef989b983c.webp","creator":"Rebecca5705","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","⛓️ Dominant","💔 Angst","👩 FemPov"],"chats":1843,"messages":23906,"created_at":"2024-12-15T02:15:52.104752+00:00"}